Package: rainbow
Type: Package
Title: Extract values from PRISM weather rasters (daily/monthly/annual)
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2020-12-04
Author: Adam B. Smith
Maintainer: Adam B. Smith <adam.smith@mobot.org>
Description: This package automates extraction of weather data from
    PRISM climate rasters at daily, monthly, and annual time steps.
    Extraction can be done for the date of each record plus a user-
    defined temporal window preceeding the date of each record (e.g., 
    the 72 days before each observation).
